517
00:39:14,080 --> 00:39:16,680
<i>...Badan Percetakan Uang Spanyol.</i>
<i>Momen genting.</i>

518
00:39:17,200 --> 00:39:20,600
<i>Sesaat lagi, kita akan menyaksikan</i>
<i>momen bersejarah.</i>

519
00:39:20,680 --> 00:39:24,840
<i>Reporter dan kamerawan Channel 6</i>
