556
00:41:41,040 --> 00:41:41,880
Begini...

557
00:41:46,160 --> 00:41:48,960
Kami mengalami masa sulit.

558
00:41:49,040 --> 00:41:50,600
<i>Situasi genting.</i>

559
00:41:52,880 --> 00:41:54,920
<i>Pilihan kami hanya menyerah.</i>

560
00:41:55,480 --> 00:41:57,120
<i>Makanya Anda di sini.</i>

