571
00:42:51,920 --> 00:42:53,520
Buka pintunya!

572
00:42:57,240 --> 00:42:59,680
<i>Sebelas dilepas. Kita saksikan langsung.</i>

573
00:42:59,760 --> 00:43:03,880
Mereka keluar.
