630
00:46:46,920 --> 00:46:49,280
<i>Pagi itu kami populer di seluruh dunia.</i>

631
00:46:49,880 --> 00:46:52,400
<i>Orang-orang terdiam</i>
<i>di kafetaria dan taksi.</i>

632
00:46:52,480 --> 00:46:55,040
<i>Kata Fonollosa, polisi berbohong.</i>

633
00:46:55,120 --> 00:46:58,320
<i>Bahwa mereka mencemari media</i>
<i>tentang masa lalunya,</i>

634
00:46:58,600 --> 00:47:01,000
<i>menantang mereka membawa berkas hukum.</i>

635
00:47:01,080 --> 00:47:04,160
<i>Kami Kamerun,</i>
