636
00:47:04,840 --> 00:47:06,520
<i>Semua orang mendukung kami.</i>

637
00:47:06,600 --> 00:47:10,760
<i>Kini kami menuju rekan berita kami,</i>
<i>Cristina Saavedra. Silakan.</i>

638
00:47:10,840 --> 00:47:14,680
<i>Kabar terbaru, Deputi Inspektur</i>
